snippet.title: Cynthia G
snippet.description: Lets get the conversation poppin on how we can repair the black relationship. This is all about empowerment and the issue that we face as a community, especially with regard to black relationships.. We will discuss interracial dating, stereotypes and the media's agenda to destroy black relationships.
